&lt;ul class=&quot;ak-ul&quot; data-indent-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;4311&quot;&gt;New hire stock equity (RSUs) and employee stock purchase plan (ESPP)&lt;/p&gt;
